Hodell-Natco  
Extensive Product Line








By offering one of the most extensive product lines in the industry and skillfully tracking down scarce items, Hodell-Natco is capable of supporting your most challenging product needs.  With a massive inventory of more than 40,000 industrial fastener and chain items, we are able to accommodate both inch and metric standard and specialty products.  Plus, we can provide most items in a variety of materials and finishes.
The following categories encompass our product offering.  Click on a category to get more product details or contact us  to learn how we can provide the best products for your needs.
