Real Customers. Real Partners.What Our Clients Say






Hodell-Natco is everything you want a supplier to be – flexible, efficient, honest, and always ‘right on’. Based on our special requests, they have bent over backwards to do things they weren’t used to doing to serve our needs. On a scale from 1  to 10, Hodell-Natco is definitely a 10!
Jeff S.Benson Woodworking



Hodell-Natco can be trusted to complete orders quickly and accurately.  We never have to double-check their deliveries. They are always well-packaged, tagged correctly, and arrive in a timely manner. Hodell-Natco makes our lives easier!
 Keith V.Mainline Supply



We consistently receive parts from   Hodell-Natco with zero defects. In fact, we’re so confident in the   quality of the parts we receive from Hodell-Natco that we no longer   waste time inspecting them ourselves. They go right into stock, saving   us valuable time!
Mark W.Parker Hannifin



As with any large and complex construction project, we encountered several problems throughout the building process.  What I liked most about working with Hodell-Natco was their unique problem-solving capabilities and their willingness to help – no matter what the problem was.
Gene M.CMC



We have great relationships with the sales staff at Hodell-Natco! The products we need are always available and the convenience of their Sparks, Nevada location makes it easy for us to pick-up product as needed.
Derek E.Vortex Steel



I’m impressed by the breadth of Hodell-Natco’s   inventory – even when I request large quantities or hard-to-find items,   they can still deliver. They regularly have product on hand to meet our   immediate needs which saves our company valuable warehouse space and   money!
Reid W.National Sales Company



Hodell-Natco is by far one of the   best customer service organizations around. The parts we need are being   manufactured in the USA and that speaks volumes to our organization. The   sales staff is friendly and knowledgeable and really wants to   understand our business and meet our needs. If you are looking for a   supplier of fasteners and other materials, you can count on   Hodell-Natco.
Bruce SAccountant/PurchaserAgriDry LLC



The personalized service I get from Hodell-Natco makes them stand out among other fastener suppliers.  I don’t have to wait for days to get a response; they get back to me immediately!  I truly appreciate their quick response time and how they help our company live up to the service standards we strive to provide our customers.
Sandy P.Materials ManagerCBC Steel Buildings



We serve general contractors and construction businesses in Northeast Ohio with plumbing and pipe equipment, and Hodell-Natco has been our fastener supplier for over 30 years!  We continue to do business with Hodell-Natco because of their broad product line, their responsiveness to our requests, and the convenience of having a reliable, local supplier.
Steve D. Jr.Lakeside Supply



Being in the structural steel fabrication business, we often estimate projects three or four months before they begin construction. Since material prices are constantly increasing, it can be challenging to accurately approximate our costs when bidding for jobs. Hodell-Natco is a preferred supplier of ours because of their fair pricing strategies. Even when prices go up, they will hold their pricing for us for up to a year! Hodell-Natco helps take the stress out of our bidding process.
Bob C.Henderson Fabrication



















